    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s just exhausting. carrying all this heaviness every day just to feel nothing. sometimes i wonder if being a ghost is actually worse than just... being gone. like, would it be easier to just stop trying to be anything at all? to just not have to carry the weight of existing?",
